name: Real Diving 3D
description:
Jump down the highest and most dangerous cliffs all over the world! Real Diving is the world's #1 realistic 3D cliff diving game!

Perform amazing acrobatics including backflips, frontflips, and gainers from the cliffs into the sea below. Timing is crucial for the divers and don’t hit the rock! Your skill and imagination are the only limits to the tricks you can pull off!

Game Features:
- Realistic physics and stunning 3D graphics
- Many sets of clothes for dozens of different divers
- Hundred of diving tricks including layouts, reverses, pikes and etc.
